[UNKNOWN] oprosti nam naše grijehe.

299
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:18,480
[UNKNOWN] Oči da je nas od katka dobrovne i da veli braje sve duše,

300
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:23,640
[UNKNOWN] osobito one koji je najpotrednije, koji je bilo svično.

301
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] U drugoj desetici razmišljat ćemo o Mariji,

302
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:38,640
[SPEAKER_00] koja posreduje osvobadjanju od grešnih vezanosti,

303
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,359
[SPEAKER_00] od tog robstva greha.

304
00:24:43,359 --> 00:25:03,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kad su donosili Isusa, Josip i Marija, prikazati ga,

305
00:25:03,759 --> 00:25:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] kako to propisuje zakon u hram,

306
00:25:09,819 --> 00:25:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] i kad su ga susreli oni koji su ga iščekivali,

307
00:25:13,299 --> 00:25:15,140
[SPEAKER_00] a posebno starac Šimon,

308
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:21,299
[SPEAKER_00] Josip i Marija su se divili

309
00:25:21,299 --> 00:25:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] o riječima kojim je izgovorio.

310
00:25:27,299 --> 00:25:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ih je Šimon blagoslovio i rekao Mariji,

311
00:25:32,619 --> 00:25:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] majci njegovi,

312
00:25:34,279 --> 00:25:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] ova je evo postavljena propast i uzdignućem nogima u Izraelu

313
00:25:42,779 --> 00:25:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] i za znak o sporavanju,

314
00:25:44,259 --> 00:25:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] a tebi će samo i mač probosti dušu,

315
00:25:52,420 --> 00:25:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] da se razotkriju namisli novi srdaca.

316
00:25:59,259 --> 00:26:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] u ovoj desetici razmatrat ćemo te riječi,

317
00:26:04,579 --> 00:26:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] a tebi će samo i mač probosti dušu,

318
00:26:09,859 --> 00:26:13,640
[SPEAKER_00] da se razotkriju namisli novi srdaca.

319
00:26:16,740 --> 00:26:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] To se zaista i dogodilo

320
00:26:19,099 --> 00:26:22,539
