329
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:59,240
[SPEAKER_00] nego ga je pratila na putu spasenja svijeta

330
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:04,200
[SPEAKER_00] i s njime podijelila agoniju smrti

331
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:07,279
[SPEAKER_00] kojim je otkupljen svijet.

332
00:27:07,279 --> 00:27:13,700
[SPEAKER_00] I što znači da se razotkriju namisli novi srdaca?

333
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] U trenutku kad je

334
00:27:18,779 --> 00:27:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] završio

335
00:27:20,259 --> 00:27:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] čin otkupljenja,

336
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] Marija je znala da će se

337
00:27:26,619 --> 00:27:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] srca svih ljudi

338
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] morati očitovati

339
00:27:30,819 --> 00:27:34,200
[SPEAKER_00] za ili protiv Isusa.

340
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tako se i ti, brate i sestro, moraš očitovati

341
