1034
00:57:33,739 --> 00:57:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] Sirah u trećem poglavju

1035
00:57:39,739 --> 00:57:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] izgovora ovu misao

1036
00:57:43,739 --> 00:57:45,739
