1037
00:57:45,739 --> 00:57:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jer blagoslovočev učvrstjuje kuću djeci

1038
00:57:50,739 --> 00:57:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] a majčina kletva temelje im ruši

1039
00:57:54,739 --> 00:57:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] ranjenost od majke

1040
00:57:59,739 --> 00:58:05,739
[SPEAKER_00] može uzdrmati naše temelje

1041
00:58:05,739 --> 00:58:13,739
