1072
01:00:42,739 --> 01:00:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] kao da konstantno osjećaš neki grč

1073
01:00:47,739 --> 01:00:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] možda je uzrok baš tome

1074
01:00:50,739 --> 01:00:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] što je tvoja majka

1075
01:00:52,739 --> 01:00:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] bila često nervozna

